  "body": "On the wiki for this project, the script for mining only when there are transactions fails sometimes, particularly when running 'truffle migrate'.  It can be fixed for the truffle case by changing the line:\r\n\r\nif (eth.getBlock(\"pending\").transactions.length > 0) {\r\n\r\nto:\r\n\r\nif (eth.pendingTransactions.length > 0) {\r\n\r\nThe former call returns 0 sometimes even when eth.pendingTransactions.length > 0.\r\n\r\nThe URL is here: https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/wiki/bitchin-tricks",
